invalid type: string "6.\n\n**Status assignment** — the record receives a KYC status that every\n   intermediary can query using the investor's PAN.\n\n## KYC statuses\n\n- **KYC Validated**: all attributes (PAN, mobile, email) verified by the\n  KRA. The investor can transact with ANY intermediary without redoing KYC.\n- **KYC Registered / Verified**: the record exists and documents are in\n